<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>URGENT: WhatsApp Session Disconnected</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #333; 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f0e8;
    }
    .header { 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b2635, #a63d4a); 
      padding: 30px; 
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
    }
    .header h1 { 
      color: #ffffff; 
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content { 
      background: #ffffff; 
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .alert-box {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      color: #856404;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .btn { 
      display: inline-block; 
      padding: 14px 32px; 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d5a27, #4a7c44); 
      color: #ffffff; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 30px; 
      color: #666; 
      font-size: 13px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🌿 FRESH HARVEST</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <h2 style="color: #8b2635; margin-top: 0;">⚠️ URGENT: WhatsApp Disconnected</h2>
    
    <div class="alert-box">
      <strong>Action Required!</strong> The WhatsApp session for Fresh Harvest Grocery has been disconnected.
    </div>
    
    <p>This means:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Order notifications will not be sent to customers</li>
      <li>Admin alerts for new orders are disabled</li>
      <li>Phone verification codes cannot be sent</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p><strong>Please take immediate action:</strong></p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="https://freshharvest.app/admin/settings/whatsapp" class="btn">Reconnect WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
    
    <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
      To reconnect:<br>
      1. Log in to the admin dashboard<br>
      2. Go to Settings → WhatsApp<br>
      3. Click "Connect" and scan the QR code with your phone
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p><strong>Fresh Harvest Grocery</strong></p>
    <p>Nairobi, Kenya | orders@freshharvest.app | 0113 323 234</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
